商业底牌」，企图继续含糊其词中「牟暴利」。 实际在 2019 年，有关部门就发文要求网约车平台企业主动公开定价机制，保持加价标准合理且相对稳定。直到现在，仍然没有一家网约车平台就抽成问题向公众给出合理解释。 网约车平台抽成比例可以在阳光下「计算」，但不能在暗地里「算计」。有关管理部门也应该为所当为。新华热评：网约车平台，请给公众一个解释"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-567b821698c145042e41badde9adb30e_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "184 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/458224652"}}, "attached_info": "ClQI7qDdr5HGuoplEAMaCDY0MTA4MDQ0IIiJ1IQGMAE4L0AUcgk0NTgyMjQ2NTJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1620443272.9147959", "card_id": "Q_451758003", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 73}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "实验室有人用服务器挖矿该怎么办?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "前一阵子 eth 大涨，然后实验室服务器天天被占用后发现是有人用服务器挖矿，目前只有我发现了，该怎么办。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-9a537ed29ce3b7aec08857c20066b7b0_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "184 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/451758003"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I7qDdr5HGuoplEAMaCDYyNjcwMDE2ILCjgoMGMAw44gRAFXIJNDUxNzU4MDAzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "22_1620443272.9152079", "card_id": "Q_453538698", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 40}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "普通话考试最后一题可以直接背百度上的范文吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "会有查重吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-ec8416b4704f8a630b1be803d598026a_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "141 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/453538698"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I7qDdr5HGuoplEAMaCDYzMDY1ODkyIMrCuoMGMAA4iwJAFnIJNDUzNTM4Njk4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "23_1620443272.91562